nodes.text: Hors d'oeuvre was a type of dish generally served before a meal. Stuffed Plavonian starfish and raw rockfish twist were popular types of hors d'oeuvre that were served aboard the luxury repulsortrain Gem of Alderaan and at the annual Vor-cal Feast held aboard the House Melantha Orbital Hunting Lodge over the planet Vycinyth. Hors d'oeuvre were served at Jabba's Palace by R4 droids, and were a favorite of Max Rebo.
